  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: App crashes when giving the camera access to scan QR code. @flexsurfer has noticed that on his `Xiaomi Redmi Note 3`. It was done when app was launched for the 1st time after install. After that it is not reproducible.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nno crashes\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n`java.lang.RuntimeException: getParameters failed (empty parameters)\r\n\tat android.hardware.Camera.native_getParameters(Native Method)\r\n\tat android.hardware.Camera.getParameters(Camera.java:1984)\r\n\tat com.lwansbrough.RCTCamera.RCTCamera.adjustPreviewLayout(RCTCamera.java:396)\r\n\tat com.lwansbrough.RCTCamera.RCTCamera.setActualDeviceOrientation(RCTCamera.java:194)\r\n\tat com.lwansbrough.RCTCamera.RCTCameraView.setActualDeviceOrientation(RCTCameraView.java:130)\r\n\tat com.lwansbrough.RCTCamera.RCTCameraView.access$100(RCTCameraView.java:16)\r\n\tat com.lwansbrough.RCTCamera.RCTCameraView$1.onOrientationChanged(RCTCameraView.java:35)\r\n\tat android.view.OrientationEventListener$SensorEventListenerImpl.onSensorChanged(OrientationEventListener.java:143)\r\n\tat android.hardware.SystemSensorManager$SensorEventQueue.dispatchSensorEvent(SystemSensorManager.java:494)\r\n\tat android.os.MessageQueue.nativePollOnce(Native Method)\r\n\tat android.os.MessageQueue.next(MessageQueue.java:323)\r\n\tat android.os.Looper.loop(Looper.java:138)\r\n\tat android.app.ActivityThread.main(ActivityThread.java:5527)\r\n\tat java.lang.reflect.Method.invoke(Native Method)\r\n\tat com.android.internal.os.ZygoteInit$MethodAndArgsCaller.run(ZygoteInit.java:739)\r\n\tat com.android.internal.os.ZygoteInit.main(ZygoteInit.java:629)`\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Give camera access to scan code\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: `0.9.10-481-g279ebc31+ (2038)`\r\n* Operating System: Android, real device Xiaomi Redmi Note 3 with custom MIU 8.5.7.0\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\nTF https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/7371377/sessions/72/?accessToken=IZccKNjSehx6Fw-mO9l917pNAWk",
